Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,#祝你生日快乐 祝你生日快乐 生日快乐#\N#Happy Birthday to you Happy Birthday to you Happy Birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,#亲爱的彭妮二十六岁生日快乐#\Ndear Penny Happy 26th birthday, Penny
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我三十了 我是个天主教堂\NI'm 30 and I'm Catholic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会自己孤单的穿着一件闪亮的圣诞毛衣死去\Nand I'm gonna die alone in a light-up Christmas sweater,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟动物园的鹦鹉去谈去吧\Ntalking to a menagerie of parrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦!\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-我现在完全摸不清头脑了 -我知道 淡定\N-I'm so confused right now. -I know you are. Been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你会意识到...\NAnd you will realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不是今天 也许也不是明天\Nmay not be today, may not be tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,或者不是从现在开始的一个月 一年...\Nmay not be a month from now or a year from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是终有一天 你会意识到\NBut you will wake up one day and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"哇 哥喜欢男淫"\N"Whoa. I like dudes."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真的那样的话 我很乐意你打电话给我\NAnd when that happens, I would love it if you gave me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以一起去喝杯 然后看场电影神马的\NWe'll go get a beer. We'll rent a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可能看"凯特和利奥波德"神马的\NMaybe "Kate & Leopold."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 我是直的 好吧?\NDude, I'm not gay, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真是个十足的恐同深柜\NWhoa. What a homophobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一个有我号码的恐同深柜 谢谢~\NA homophobe who now has my number, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩这是天合之作\NReally excellent work, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是我过得最糟糕的生日了\NThat was my worst birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我妈跟我前男友在假日乐园舌吻那次之后\Nsince my mom frenched my boyfriend at Epcot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你百分之百确定托德是个同性恋?\NSo are you 100% sure Todd is gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,百分之一百五\N-150%.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们昨天晚上告别的时候有点诡异\NOur good-bye last night was a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 拜\NOh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有人跟戴夫和阿历克斯谈过吗\NHas anyone talked to Dave or Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 戴夫就来了\NYeah, Dave's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们就不能叫阿历克斯了\N-So that means we can't invite Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真是糟透了\NWow. This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘿 大伙 看呐 嗯哼? -嗨 各位\N-Hey, guys. Check it out.  Huh? -Hi, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好消息吧?\NRight? Great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们破镜重圆了 开玩笑的\NWe are back together. Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是很讨厌她\NI still hate her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过看在她昨晚花四个小时跟哥道歉的份上\Nbut she did spend four hours apologizing last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-这真是个好的开始 -戴夫承认\N-which was a pretty good start.  -And Dave did admit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他把我的存在当做理所当然的事了\Nthat he's been taking me for granted for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我承认\N- I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我说过那是你应该在婚礼前谈的事\Nbut I said that's the kind of stuff you talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是在婚礼前 不是在婚礼中哦\Nbefore the wedding, not at the wedding. And I pointed out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有戴夫撒双人字拖\Nthat Dave wore flip-flops
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就去赴我父母结婚三十五周年的纪念宴会\Nto my parents' 35th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那是跟黑领带一起的混搭\NMm. It was black-tie optional.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-又来了 -另一场血雨腥风啊\N-Here we go again.  -Another double bloody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,童鞋们 这... 这都是我的错\NGuys, this is... This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我对戴夫做的一切 真是 真是太过分了\NAnd what I did to Dave was... was horrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们懂的 但是我和戴夫说好了 我俩\Nyou know, but... but Dave and I agree that that's between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这样还不如让我去死...\Nyou know, and it would kill me if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我成为大家以后不能一起混的罪魁祸首\NIf I'm the reason that we all can't hang out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是说 我们大家都没有交新朋友\NYeah, I mean, none of us has made a new friend
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去的十一年当中\Nin, like, 11 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至都不知道怎么去交朋友了\N- I wouldn't even know how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做 就像在大街上随便找个人 开始聊天\NWhat do you do, just, like, walk up to random people and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"嘿 废话一堆 喜欢体育吗?"\N"Hey, blah, blah, blah. Sports"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想认识的唯一人选就是我老公\NThe only new person I wanna meet is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一次在这里 碰到一个老女人\NI was once on this plane with this old lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她想跟我搭讪\Nand she tried talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-我就假装我残废了 -伙计\N-I just pretended I had some kind of disability. -Buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 彭妮搞砸了你的生日我很抱歉\NHey, Penny, I'm sorry your birthday got ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是人家给你准备了个惊喜\NBut I got you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘿 是什么 溜冰鞋? -呕!\N-Hey, what is it, rollerblades?  -Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我道歉\NOkay, I apologize.  Ah, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -哦哦!\N- Okay.  - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,生日快乐哟!\NHappy Birthday!  Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 自从犹太教成年礼以来\NAw! I haven't been this happy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,人家就没这么开心过\Nsince my bar mitzvah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你能坐着说话吗?\NCan you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果大家不介意的要话 我开动了\NMmm. Don't mind if I do-skis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 不会吧\NUh, maybe you don't-skis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 你就不能歇一会儿不吃蛋糕啊\NYou might want to take a little vacation from the cake, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我显胖吗?\NIs this the chubby thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 请当面告诉我\N'Cause if it is, just say it to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙觉得我胖吗?\NDo you guys think I look fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 说实话 有一点\NWell, you got a couple extra pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你挺健康的 我只在乎你的身体\N-I think about your health. -I just worry about your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 你像年轻时候的\NTo be perfectly honest, you look like
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,凯西 贝茨 (好莱坞女演员 非常丰满)\Na young Kathy Bates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 不 就像自暴自弃后暴饮暴食的Paul Rudd\NOoh. No, no, no. It's like if Paul Rudd gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就接手 人家不介意的\NI'll take her. I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-哦 你应该... -好吧\N-Oh, you're supposed to...  -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦噢!~\NWhoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,#哦 哦 哦 我喜欢她因为她独特的魅力#\N#Oh, oh, oh I love her because she moves in her own way #
